{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T10:55:54.652Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "LSTM Gates — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What LSTM Gates Are"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LSTM gates"}, {"type": "text", "text": " are the core mechanisms that allow Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks to control what information is stored, updated, or discarded as the network learns. They act like "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "filters or switches"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that regulate information flow through the LSTM cell, enabling it to maintain relevant data across many time steps."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each gate is a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "tiny decision maker"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that uses the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "sigmoid function"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (outputs 0–1) to decide how much information to keep (1 = keep) or forget (0 = discard)."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why LSTM Gates Matter in Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTM gates solve the main problem of traditional RNNs: they "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "forget too much over time"}, {"type": "text", "text": ". This enables LSTMs to:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Capability"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Application"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Remember long-term context"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Language models like ChatGPT understand entire conversations"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Capture long-term dependencies"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Process lengthy documents, multi-step reasoning"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Maintain relevant information"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Image generation, speech recognition, summarization"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Avoid vanishing gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Train effectively on long sequences"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Three Main Gates"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Forget Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Decides What to Remove)"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Details"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Decides what information from the previous cell state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_{t-1}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " should be discarded or retained"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Inputs"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Current input "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " + previous hidden state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_{t-1}"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Math"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "f_t = \\sigma(W_f \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_f)"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vector "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "f_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " with values 0–1 (same dimension as cell state)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Action"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_t \\leftarrow f_t \\odot C_{t-1}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (element-wise multiplication)"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "How it works"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- If gate outputs "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "close to 0"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"forget it\" (remove that information)\n- If gate outputs "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "close to 1"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": \"keep it\" (retain that information)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Example"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": When reading \"I love cats. The dog is too,\" the forget gate might remove information about \"love\" since it's no relevant to the new subject \"dog\"."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Helps the network get rid of "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "irrelevant details"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that could clutter its memory."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Input Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Decides What to Add)"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Details"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Controls how much new information from the current input should be added to memory"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Inputs"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Current input "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " + previous hidden state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_{t-1}"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Math"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "i_t = \\sigma(W_i \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_i)"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vector "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "i_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (0–1) that filters candidate values"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Candidate State"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\tilde{C}_t = \\tanh(W_C \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_C)"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (values −1 to +1)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Action"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_t = f_t \\odot C_{t-1} + i_t \\odot \\tilde{C}_t"}}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "How it works in 3 stages"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Candidate cell state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\tilde{C}_t"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": ": Creates potential new information using tanh (values −1 to +1)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Calculate "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "i_t"}}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": ": Decides which parts of "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\tilde{C}_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " to actually store"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Update cell state"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Add filtered new information to memory"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Example"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": When reading \"The cat jumps,\" the input gate adds \"cat\" and \"jumps\" to long-term memory."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Network learns to update memory with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "relevant new data"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (Decides What to Reveal)"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Details"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Determines what information from the current cell state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "C_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " should be sent to the next step"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Inputs"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Current input "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "x_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " + previous hidden state "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_{t-1}"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Math"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "o_t = \\sigma(W_o \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_o)"}}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Vector "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "o_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " (0–1) that filters cell state"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Action"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t = o_t \\odot \\tanh(C_t)"}}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "How it works"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n1. Calculate "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "o_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " via sigmoid (filter values 0–1)\n2. Pass cell state through tanh (scale to −1 to +1)\n3. Multiply: "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "h_t = o_t \\odot \\tanh(C_t)"}}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Purpose"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Decides which parts of memory to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "reveal as output"}, {"type": "text", "text": ". The output becomes the input for the next step in the sequence."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How All Gates Work Together"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The complete LSTM cell:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "text"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTM Cell Components:\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Cell State (C_t): Long-term memory      │\n│ Hidden State (h_t): Short-term memory   │\n│ Forget Gate (f_t): What to remove       │\n│ Input Gate (i_t): What to add           │\n│ Output Gate (o_t): What to reveal       │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nStep-by-step process:\n\n1. FORGET gate decides what to remove:\n   f_t = σ(W_f · [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_f)\n   C_t_temp = f_t ⊙ C_{t-1}\n\n2. INPUT gate decides what to add:\n   i_t = σ(W_i · [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_i)\n   C̃_t = tanh(W_C · [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_C)\n   C_t = C_t_temp + i_t ⊙ C̃_t\n\n3. OUTPUT gate decides what to reveal:\n   o_t = σ(W_o · [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_o)\n   h_t = o_t ⊙ tanh(C_t)\n\n4. Output h_t goes to next time step"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "All gates work together to maintain the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "cell state"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (long-term memory). The gates control how this memory is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "updated, kept, or cleared"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTM Architecture Diagram"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "yaml"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "                    ┌───────────────────┐\nCurrent Input: x_t ─▶│                   │\n                    │   Forget Gate     │ f_t = σ(...)\nPrevious State:h_t-1▶│   Input Gate      │ i_t = σ(...)\n                    │   Output Gate     │ o_t = σ(...)\n                    │                   │\nCell State:    C_t-1▶│   Cell State      │ C_t = ...\n                    │   (Long-term mem) │\n                    └───────────────────┘\n                            │\n                            ▼\n                    ┌───────────────────┐\n                    │   Hidden State    │ h_t = ...\n                    │  (Short-term mem) │\n                    └───────────────────┘\n                            │\n                            ▼\n                        Output: h_t"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Differences: Gates vs. Traditional RNN"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Property"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Traditional RNN"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTM with Gates"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memory control"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "No control; passive decay"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Active control via 3 gates"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Long-term memory"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Limited (vanishes)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Strong (cell state C_t)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Information flow"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fixed"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Regulated by gates"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Vanishing gradient"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Severe problem"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Solved by gating"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefits of LSTM Gates"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefit"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Selectively forget"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Remove irrelevant information to prevent clutter"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Selectively add"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Store only relevant new information"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Selectively reveal"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Output only useful parts of memory"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Long-term memory"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Maintain cell state across many time steps"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solves vanishing gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gates prevent gradient decay"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental Model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of LSTM gates as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "smart notebook"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Forget Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You decide which old notes to throw out (remove irrelevant info)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Input Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You decide which new notes to write down (add important info)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": You decide which notes to read aloud (reveal useful info)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Or think of it as a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "coffee shop manager"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Forget Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Fires employees who don't help (remove bad workers)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Input Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Hires new employees who are skilled (add good workers)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output Gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Assigns tasks based on employee skills (use best workers)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "GRU Gates (Simplified Version)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "GRU (Gated Recurrent Unit) has only "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "2 gates"}, {"type": "text", "text": " instead of 3:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "GRU Gate"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Function"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Reset Gate"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Combines forget + part of input gate functions"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Update Gate"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Decides what to update and what to keep"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Advantage"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Simpler architecture with fewer parameters, but similar performance to LSTM."}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LSTM gates"}, {"type": "text", "text": " are 3 decision mechanisms (forget, input, output) that control information flow"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each gate uses "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "sigmoid"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (outputs 0–1) to decide how much to keep (1) or forget (0)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Forget gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Decides what to remove from long-term memory"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Input gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Decides what new information to add to memory (uses tanh for candidates)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Output gate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Decides what information to reveal as output to next step"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gates work together to maintain "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "cell state"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (long-term memory) across many time steps"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTM gates "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "solve vanishing gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": " by actively controlling what to remember/forget"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTMs enable "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ChatGPT, speech recognition, and summarization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " by remembering context over long sequences"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LSTM gates are the mechanisms that let networks "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "decide what information to keep or discard"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", solving the main problem of traditional RNNs that forget too much over time."}]}]}}